wikipedia_page.main: Sir John Strachan (died 28 December 1777) was a Baronet and chief of Clan Strachan.  He served in the Royal Navy, rising to the rank of captain and commanding a number of warships.  His nephew, Richard Strachan, would also go on to have a distinguished career in the Navy.

response: *Sir John Strachan, 5th Baronet (died 1777), captain in the Royal Navy
